---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Support — Praetor by Katafract"
  description="Praetor support. Coming soon with Sovereign subscription."
  ogDescription="Praetor is in development. Support documentation coming when the app enters TestFlight."
  section="prose"
>
  <link slot="head" rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />

  <div class="prose-header">
    <p class="prose-eyebrow">Praetor &mdash; Support</p>
    <h1>Praetor Support</h1>
    <p class="prose-meta">Katafract LLC &mdash; Coming with Sovereign &mdash; <a href="//support">All app support &rarr;</a></p>
  </div>

  <div class="prose-body">

    <div class="callout">
      <p>Praetor is in development. Full support documentation, FAQs, and troubleshooting guides will be published when Praetor enters TestFlight. In the meantime, we're here to help with any pre-release questions.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Get Help</h2>
    <p>Have questions about Praetor or ready to test early? Reach out anytime:</p>
    <div class="contact-card">
      <h3>Support Inquiries</h3>
      <p>Katafract LLC</p>
      <p><a href="mailto:hello@katafract.com">hello@katafract.com</a></p>
      <p>We typically respond within one business day.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</Base>
